{"tid":1707764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"核爆都唔割呀！！！","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:22:41.000Z","uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7beb3889d55c78cd1af0f910bee9bba0c7ca3c","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:20:05.000Z","msg":"成撚日話「放核彈都唔割」「核爆都唔割」<br />\n今日下晝就有個火魔<br />\n都未係放炸彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BBQ咋</span></span><br />\n你班PK就係到出PO話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「你咁樣同班POPO有咩分別呀？」</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「要同佢割蓆！！！」</span></span><br />\n係撚咁話要割蓆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">割撚到張蓆就嚟唔見左啦變撚番原子啦！！！<br />\n仲割！！！</span></span><br />\n人地藍屍拎棍拎刀周街打開車撞人都冇人話過要割啦<br />\n你地就核彈都未出就係撚咁割，<span style=\"color: red;\">仲仆街過啲藍屍呀屌你！</span><br />\n<br />\n講多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割呀！！！</span></span><br />\n邊個再割就割埋你條撚呀"},{"pid":"b4cbe925fcb7fe98fb0688efe3166bb9c261a974","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:21:08.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割呀！！！"},{"pid":"7a7046f1f0921df0e653473ba5bcfe9838df9548","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:21:18.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割呀！！！"},{"pid":"d55ed405e8deb97d36de90b0bd2435239f4a416f","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割呀！！！"},{"pid":"938a15cfd6686454c9d94697dbf6f6cea6deba91","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割呀！！！"},{"pid":"9010347fa883ffcc034706f0170d1422e4854be6","tid":1707764,"uid":313466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割呀！！！"},{"pid":"3d71